column5: well after the bacon left again at noon to find the fish...after getting stuck yesterday coming off the lake decided against the sled and took buddies wheeler....here's what happened.... Little more aqua on dee lake...   First fish...   Water is actually flowing into the holes...   The result and my favourite pic!!!!

Excellent!  Nice Lakers Dale.  Thats a fine looking scooter you got there, i gots to get one of those......i've got $62 canadian tire money....lol....a ways to go yet.  Wabigoon was snow covered when i left for work on Sunday morning....by the time i got home we also had a little more water "on dee lake"....lol.
